Build instructions for libsomanetwork. 

NOTE: In general, you should use one of the pre-built debs for most
Soma software, including this library.

BUILD REQUIREMENTS:
cmake
Boost 1.37.0
sigc++-2.0 for the benchmarks

These packages are available from the Ubuntu package archive.

Typically, building can be accomplished with : 

cmake
make
make test
sudo make install

